title: Aggrestsuko Season 2 Idea
body:
Hey so came up with this idea after watching the season 2 trailer.

Spoilers below for season 2 trailer

Ok so we see that Retsuko’s mom… well doesn’t seem great (incredibly overbearing and controlling), also that Ton is making Retsuko supervise Anai so came up with and idea and 2 ways it could go down..

Ok so while that’s going on Retsuko is having to deal with her mother trying to force her into an arranged marriage and also undermining her carer because ‘you should be married and a housewife’ and eventually Retsuko finally tells her mother she is not getting married.

Retsuko’s mother starts ranting and  Retsuko reaches her breaking point and just snaps full on Aggretsuko shocking her mother and then after she calmly tells her ‘no I’m not getting married goodbye mother I have work to do” and Ton overheard and is just gaping like holy sh@t that’s amazing and then Retsuko is overloaded with work as Ton ties to get her to snap like what if Ton getting Retsuko to train Anai, is because he’s kind of training her up for leadership role /seeing how she copes in it like everyone thinks he’s just forcing more responsibilities on her to torture her but he’s really like that ball of rage is the only one I trust be my replacement and I make her be assertive enough to do it even if it kills me.

Basically Ton actually trying to mentor an oblivious Retsuko.

(I love the idea of Retusko being the boss and Haida being like the stay at home dad)
